Name: Battle Imagine - Tina
Description:
Use to activate or upgrade Tina's Battle Imagine skill: Arcane! Time Decree.

Arcane! Time Decree
Summon Tina to infuse time power into Allies, granting them CD reduction effect for a period.
(Cannot be affected by the same type of effect within 100s)
